MAC Spoofing:
â€¢	MAC spoofing is a technique used to change the MAC address of a network interface to a different value.

1. Check Current MAC Address : macchanger -s <interface>

2. Set a Random MAC Address: macchanger -a <interface>

3. Set a Specific MAC Address: macchanger -m <macid> <interface>

4. List MAC Vendor Names: macchanger -l / --list

5. Reverts to the original MAC address of the interface.: macchanger -p <interface>
